It's the first episode of the Major Issues Podcast for 2023, and boy do we have a lot coming to us this year in the form of comics, movies, and television shows! Its become a yearly tradition to break down our expectations of the projects set to be released in the next 12 months so join us as we do our best to PREDICT 2023! If you can, please leave us a review on [ITunes](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us where ever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our merchandise! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by ComicBook Clique, the only stop for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media. Send us feedback at ComicBookClique@Gmail.com! You Are Worthy! 

